#Jordan P.

#### Read about Jordan and investigate the audit logs. Can you find any evidence of fraud?

**[Click here](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1GRBeFTM2ZnkZnTbZs6TPJsKO7Yu0ZBIbYnFX1nMiwwQ/edit?usp=sharing) if you would prefer to view the audit logs in a document.**

---
## User Profile
* **Age**: 17
* **Location**: Lives in Sacramento, CA with their aunt and younger sibling
* **School**: Attends school from 8:30 AM–3:30 PM
* **Work**: Part-time job at a smoothie shop (evenings)
* **Devices**: iPhone 14 (mobile), Chromebook (school-issued)
* **Tech Habits**: Logs in from home Wi-Fi or school; never uses public computers
* **Spending Habits**: Pays with Apple Pay or debit card, usually at local shops and food places; rarely shops online
* **Hobbies**: Fitness, drawing, local volunteering (animal shelter)
* **Travel History**: Never left California; doesn’t drive yet
* **Security Habits**: Uses Face ID and MFA; same password for 5+ years across all accounts


---
